{
  "texts": [
    "These novel disclosure standards would contribute to embedding these AI polling technologies into \"an institutional infrastructure that secures reason by providing accessibility\" (Beckman et al. 2022)-thereby endowing AI polling with democratic legitimacy.",
    "We contend that AI polls cannot compromise on the value of explicability.",
    "This should guide policy-making.",
    "Coming back to the example of the campaign of misinformation, we envision that a real-time auditing of the dubious AI pollster would reveal the biased nature of the machine.",
    "We expect the pollster to experience a loss of credibility as a result of this inquiry, which would defeat the attempt at manipulation."
  ]
}